    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is an ideal choice for someone looking for a dependable daily driver at an accessible price point. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable door dings, some clear coat peeling on the roof, and minor scuffs on the bumpers. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and visible wear on the driver's seat bolster, though all electronics and the air conditioning remain fully functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, although it will likely need new brake pads and a suspension tune-up in the near future. It is a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
