    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and I think you're going to love it! It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily drives. It runs smooth, looks great, and I've taken really good care of it over the years. It's the perfect ride for someone who wants something dependable and ready to hit the road immediately. Come check it out and take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure it'll put a smile on your face!",
      "price": 31500.0,
